        <num>CC 2367.2</num>
        <heading>2367.2.  Component parts of separate property</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 2367.2.  Component parts of separate property
When a spouse with his own separate property incorporates in or attaches to a separate immovable of the other spouse things that become component parts under Articles 465 and 466, Article 2367.1 applies.</p>
        </content>
